- Favourites: Create your favourites list by clicking on the heart icon on the map view, including your most visited destinations or the bus stops or bus routes you use regularly. Service updates notifications of your favourite routes and bus stops will appear on your Tallinja App informing you of any diversions happening on specific days. Include your most frequent routes and bus stops as ‘Favourites’ to be able to access your route in one tap. A heart icon next to your favourite bus stop will appear, indicating that this bus stop is on your ‘Favourites’ list.
